name: Bro
description: It’s Bro, Inspired by Dima Buterin's tweet and it's your crypto homie and the Internet's most used slang Why stress, dude? Bro’s all about chillin’ and cruisin’ through crypto. No rush, no panic. Just vibes. Whether you’re holding bags or checking out the scene, Bro’s here to keep things easy. Take it slow, relax, and let Bro show you the smooth path to crypto, man. It will bring you big thing soon.
